videos.headline: Browne finds Moss for 48-yard TD
videos.description: Max Browne throws a strike to Chawntez Moss for 48 yards and the touchdown to put Pittsburgh on the board.

videos.headline: Ollison marches in for TD
videos.description: RB Qadree Ollison extends Pittsburgh's lead with a 10- yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Rice's Ibe forces and recovers the fumble at goal line
videos.description: DB J.T. Ibe saves a potential touchdown run at the goal line by forcing and recovering a fumble from Pittsburgh's RB Chawntez Moss.

videos.headline: Moss sneaks in for 1-yard TD
videos.description: Pittsburgh extends there lead on RB Chawntez Moss' one-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Walter jets past defenders for 70-yard TD catch
videos.description: Rice QB Jackson Tyner finds Austin Walter who outraces defenders for a 70-yard touchdown in third quarter.

videos.headline: Weah leaps over defensive back for 30-yard gain
videos.description: Max Browne throws it up to Jester Weah who makes a leaping 30-yard catch.

videos.headline: Browne finds Hall who keeps foot in-bounds for 1-yard TD catch
videos.description: Max Browne completes a short pass to Darrin Hall who gets a foot in for the touchdown.

videos.headline: Tyner finds Granson on the sideline for leaping 27-yard catch
videos.description: Kylen Granson goes up and makes the catch over the defensive back for a 27-yard catch.

videos.headline: Browne finds Clark on 7-yard TD pass
videos.description: Max Browne completes a  7-yard pass to Chris Clark for Browne's fourth touchdown pass of the day.
